name: My fake vacation
body:
My Wonderful Week in Wonderland

I recently spend a week in Wonderland. Wonderland is a city in Mysterworld.

Activities

I had the pleasure of trying out lots of great local divertisements, including:

  • Chasing wabbits
  • Drinking potions
  • Eating mushrooms
  • Drinking tea

Celebrity Encounters

Richard Simmons!
